2026-04-24T18:34:28.0048567Z #14 8.783 - `python#.#-dev`: includes development headers for building C extensions
2026-04-24T18:34:28.0049175Z #14 8.783 - `python#.#-venv`: provides the standard library `venv` module
2026-04-24T18:34:28.0049778Z #14 8.783 - `python#.#-distutils`: provides the standard library `distutils` module
2026-04-24T18:34:28.0050525Z #14 8.783 - `python#.#-lib2to3`: provides the `2to3-#.#` utility as well as the standard library `lib2to3` module
2026-04-24T18:34:28.0051252Z #14 8.783 - `python#.#-gdbm`: provides the standard library `dbm.gnu` module
2026-04-24T18:34:28.0051819Z #14 8.783 - `python#.#-tk`: provides the standard library `tkinter` module
